WEBVTT

00:01.567 --> 00:04.119
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:04.120 --> 00:06.721
This is the third time we've
been here in two weeks, Sam.

00:06.721 --> 00:08.573
Any idea why you're having
so many fights?

00:08.574 --> 00:11.426
Yeah, yeah, ever since that
biker bar closed down,

00:11.427 --> 00:13.061
we're getting these
big apes coming in here.

00:13.062 --> 00:14.379
I mean, what are
we supposed to do?

00:14.380 --> 00:16.062
Be grateful.

00:18.667 --> 00:19.801
You know something,

00:19.802 --> 00:21.636
if you'd get over here
when I called you,

00:21.637 --> 00:24.005
none of this would've happened.

00:24.039 --> 00:25.740
Oh, oh, look at this.

00:25.741 --> 00:27.441
Woody. Oh, man,
are you all right?

00:27.442 --> 00:28.843
Yeah, I'm okay.

00:28.844 --> 00:30.980
See, this is exactly
what I'm talking about.

00:30.981 --> 00:33.014
We're gonna have to
file an injury report.

00:33.015 --> 00:35.267
You bet you are.
Tell him, tell him what happened.

00:35.268 --> 00:37.735
Well, I was downstairs
getting a case of scotch,

00:37.736 --> 00:39.971
and there's that
one low beam...

00:40.022 --> 00:42.541
What happened here?

00:45.244 --> 00:46.995
(theme song begins)

00:49.348 --> 00:51.366
♪ Sometimes you want to go ♪

00:51.400 --> 00:54.736
♪ Where everybody
knows your name ♪

00:56.805 --> 01:01.375
♪ And they're always
glad you came ♪

01:01.410 --> 01:03.778
♪ You wanna be
where you can see ♪

01:03.813 --> 01:06.348
♪ Our troubles
are all the same ♪

01:06.382 --> 01:10.685
♪ You wanna go where
everybody knows your name. ♪

